PostScript to HPGL converter for pen plotters.

__Usage__
./plot.sh <inFile>

Edit plot.sh with the correct port if /dev/lp0 is not usable.

__Design__
Wrapper for pstoedit ensuring correctly generated HPGL commands to drive HP DraftPlus plotter. Currently addresses landscape oriented documents.

